Console

Debug.Log("...");
Debug.LogWarning("...");
Debug.LogError("...");

NOTE:

1st is logging with a white exclamation with a message background
2nd is logging with a yellow exclamation with a triangle
3rd is logging with a red exclamation with an octagon background

LF = Line Feed

[Enabling AdvancedSavedOptions]

Tools -> Customize -> Commands -> Menubar: change to File
Add Command -> Add Advanced Saved Options 

NOTE: Using AdvancedSavedOptions -> we can turn on Windows CR LF
to turn on LF.

[Tabs vs Spaces]

Tools -> Options -> TextEditor -> All Languages -> Tabs : select keep tabs or insert spaces
C# -> Tabs: select keep tabs or insert spaces